# Data Flow - Machine Learning Pipeline

## Real-Time Data Processing

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    subgraph "Data Sources"
        API[External APIs]
        DB[Database]
        FILES[CSV/JSON Files]
        STREAM[Data Streams]
    end

    subgraph "Ingestion Layer"
        KAFKA[Apache Kafka]
        AIRFLOW[Apache Airflow]
    end

    subgraph "Processing"
        SPARK[Apache Spark]
        CLEAN[Data Cleaning]
        TRANSFORM[Feature Engineering]
        VALIDATE[Data Validation]
    end

    subgraph "ML Pipeline"
        TRAIN[Model Training]
        EVAL[Model Evaluation]
        DEPLOY[Model Deployment]
        PREDICT[Predictions]
    end

    subgraph "Storage"
        DATALAKE[(Data Lake - S3)]
        WAREHOUSE[(Data Warehouse)]
        MLFLOW[MLflow Registry]
    end

    subgraph "Output"
        DASHBOARD[Real-time Dashboard]
        ALERTS[Automated Alerts]
        REPORTS[Scheduled Reports]
    end

    API --> KAFKA
    DB --> AIRFLOW
    FILES --> AIRFLOW
    STREAM --> KAFKA

    KAFKA --> SPARK
    AIRFLOW --> SPARK

    SPARK --> CLEAN
    CLEAN --> TRANSFORM
    TRANSFORM --> VALIDATE
    VALIDATE --> DATALAKE

    DATALAKE --> TRAIN
    TRAIN --> EVAL
    EVAL --> MLFLOW
    MLFLOW --> DEPLOY
    DEPLOY --> PREDICT

    VALIDATE --> WAREHOUSE
    PREDICT --> DASHBOARD
    PREDICT --> ALERTS
    WAREHOUSE --> REPORTS
```

