# State Diagram - Order Processing

## Order States and Transitions

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Draft : Create order

    Draft --> PendingPayment : Confirm order
    Draft --> Cancelled : Cancel

    PendingPayment --> PaymentFailed : Payment rejected
    PendingPayment --> Paid : Payment successful
    PendingPayment --> Cancelled : Timeout/Cancel

    PaymentFailed --> PendingPayment : Retry payment
    PaymentFailed --> Cancelled : Cancel permanently

    Paid --> Processing : Start processing
    Processing --> InTransit : Ship
    Processing --> Cancelled : Cancel (refund)

    InTransit --> Delivered : Delivery confirmed
    InTransit --> DeliveryFailed : Delivery failed

    DeliveryFailed --> InTransit : Retry delivery
    DeliveryFailed --> ReturnToSender : Return

    Delivered --> Completed : Confirm receipt
    Delivered --> ReturnRequested : Request return

    ReturnRequested --> ReturnApproved : Approve return
    ReturnRequested --> ReturnDenied : Deny return

    ReturnApproved --> Refunded : Process refund
    ReturnDenied --> Completed : Finalize

    Cancelled --> [*]
    Completed --> [*]
    Refunded --> [*]
    ReturnToSender --> [*]

    note right of Processing
        Prepare inventory
        Generate labels
        Coordinate shipping
    end note

    note right of InTransit
        Active tracking
        Automated notifications
        Delivery estimate
    end note
```

