# Class Diagram - User Management System

## Data Model and Relationships

```mermaid
classDiagram
    class User {
        +UUID id
        +String email
        +String passwordHash
        +String firstName
        +String lastName
        +DateTime createdAt
        +DateTime updatedAt
        +Boolean isActive
        +validatePassword(password)
        +updateProfile(data)
        +deactivate()
    }

    class Role {
        +UUID id
        +String name
        +String description
        +Permission[] permissions
        +DateTime createdAt
        +addPermission(permission)
        +removePermission(permission)
        +hasPermission(action)
    }

    class Permission {
        +UUID id
        +String action
        +String resource
        +String description
        +matches(action, resource)
    }

    class Profile {
        +UUID id
        +UUID userId
        +String avatar
        +String phone
        +String address
        +JSON preferences
        +DateTime lastLoginAt
        +updateAvatar(file)
        +updatePreferences(prefs)
    }

    class Organization {
        +UUID id
        +String name
        +String slug
        +String description
        +String website
        +DateTime createdAt
        +Boolean isActive
        +addMember(user, role)
        +removeMember(user)
        +updateSettings(data)
    }

    class Membership {
        +UUID id
        +UUID userId
        +UUID organizationId
        +UUID roleId
        +DateTime joinedAt
        +Boolean isActive
        +changeRole(newRole)
        +activate()
        +deactivate()
    }

    class Session {
        +UUID id
        +UUID userId
        +String token
        +String ipAddress
        +String userAgent
        +DateTime expiresAt
        +DateTime createdAt
        +Boolean isActive
        +extend()
        +revoke()
        +isExpired()
    }

    User ||--o{ Profile : has
    User ||--o{ Session : has
    User ||--o{ Membership : has
    Organization ||--o{ Membership : has
    Role ||--o{ Membership : assigned
    Role ||--o{ Permission : contains

    User : +login(email, password)
    User : +logout()
    User : +resetPassword()
    User : +updateProfile()

    Organization : +inviteUser(email, role)
    Organization : +removeUser(userId)
    Organization : +updateMemberRole(userId, roleId)
```

